CSPORT is a platform based on blockchain solution (Web3 app) allowing athletes and their stakeholders to create and capture value through tradable assets and well being initiatives of impact with De-Fi, Social-Fi, and Game-FI dynamics.

Our purpose is “TO BRING FINANCIAL ACCESS TO THE ATHLETES OF THE FUTURE, CONNECTING THEM AND CREATING VALUE WITHIN DIFFERENT GROUPS OF STAKEHOLDERS”

Why?
Sport move passions. Talents inspire the world. And today more than ever, in a rarefied world, sport is an escape valve to believe in more. And with technology we can do it like never before.

We  are changing de game, trough different kinds of tokens, a marketplace and bundle of dynamic and unique experiences

At Csport you will be able to:

BE part of the real and epic stories
BE like an athletes and win like them
BE a partner and grow with them
BE part of a unique experience

All in a unique interaction model, connecting the real and the virtual world, in one space where only family, representative and clubs had access. With Csport it's for anyone who loves sport and the future.

Csport works trough different kinds of token (today based on Solana, then Multichain)

- CSPT. Our Governance Token. To buy, interact and governance of Csport.

- ROCKT. Our utility and “breeding”, to create value with your action “like an athletes”. Fans. investors, users interacting with athletes, through the actions performed in the real world (“MOVE & EARN”)

- ATHLETES MARKETPLACE. Where you can buy uniques pieces, an experiences that you can use and win with your athletes and his Performance. Different kinds of NFTs that we called: "X-NFT" (experiences), "3D-NFT" (digital and physical pieces) and the main NFT that create a unique dynamic on our model,  "WT-NFT" (win together NFT), that have an income-share agreements behind that NFT like a "suspensive condition" white many other things that made it unique.

- AVATAR MARKETPLACE. Where you can buy uniques pieces to create more value with your actions (well being initiatives). Every user creates value with the impact of their own actions
(Powering Move & Earn actions with “Avatar NFTs” & “Boost”).

12.short_description: We improve workplace environments by connecting professionals with jobs that can thrive through employee happiness-based recruitment.

18.description:
Did you know that 6 out of 10 digital professionals are dissatisfied with their current position?


This issue not only has an emotional impact on the professional, but it also costs companies up to 400% of the value of a monthly payroll due to low productivity and attrition.


What if I told you there was an answer?


Each individual has a distinct talent, and at each stage of their professional career, there is a job opportunity in which they can shine, and work happiness is essential to achieving it.


We are Neomadas, the first HR Tech StartUp that improves work environments by connecting digital professionals with companies where they can shine through job happiness recruitment and selection.


We developed a B2C2B business model to make this project scalable: Our ambition is to be the manager of Latam's largest digital rockstar community.


To accomplish this, we focus not only on providing good support during the selection process, but also on being available to them throughout their working lives, providing them with tools for self-awareness, professional and personal development, and all from our platform.


Digital interaction will provide us with enough information to identify talent in an unobtrusive manner, allowing us to bring you job opportunities at the right time throughout your professional life.


Unlike other companies and platforms around the world, such as Talently, Torre, Multiplica, or Michael Page, Neómadas has online tests that are taken anonymously to the leader and the close environment of the vacancy, the results of which are crossed by our AI with the information of our community, allowing us to have a more accurate person-organization affinity. Likewise, we are the first to put job happiness at the center of the Recruitment and Selection process.


We are a team of three founders: Marco Tito, a digital growth specialist with experience in StartUps such as Cabify; Sarah Cárdenas, a psychologist specialized in IT recruitment in StartUps such as Multiplica and Crehana; and Christian Revilla, a software specialist and entrepreneur of digital transformation agencies in Peru that have invoiced more than $ 1M (USD).


And together, we will create a world in which everyone, regardless of background, ethnicity, gender, or age, sees work as a second home.

12.short_description: Internet software and services

18.description:
We are a platform that combines a software asset management solution with a large marketplace where individuals can find all the software they need to work on their projects.

These tools are offered in cost-effective packages that can be tailored to specific needs.

The software, provided by our trusted partners, undergoes a thorough evaluation according to our quality standards. If approved, the software is listed, at no cost to the partner, who will receive a percentage of each package subscription in which their software is added.

Individual users subscribed to an Advanced or Expert package will automatically receive a badge. Having this will give the user access to exclusive benefits with our Partners. At the end of the subscription, the subscription will be forfeited. 

Eventually we will implement a tokenized license marketplace. On the one hand, there will be an official sales marketplace and, on the other hand, a P2P resale marketplace.

-This will allow our partners to sell licenses to companies and individuals.

-When these companies and individuals no longer need these licenses, they will be able to resell them.

-In this way, we will give control to the user of his software, who will really own his digital property, and the software producer who has listed the product will get a percentage for each resale of his license.

12.short_description: Marketing Agency

18.description:
En nuestra firma de growth marketing, desafiamos lo convencional. No somos una agencia de marketing tradicional, somos tu socio estratégico en el camino hacia el éxito. Nuestra filosofía se basa en tres pilares fundamentales que consideramos esenciales para el progreso de tu empresa: datos, plazos y comunicación.

Datos como Punto de Partida: En lugar de confiar en suposiciones, fundamentamos nuestras decisiones en los datos de tu empresa. Analizamos a fondo tus métricas, identificamos áreas de oportunidad y diseñamos estrategias precisas y efectivas que impulsen el crecimiento sostenible.Plazos Definidos para Resultados Tangibles: Entendemos que el tiempo es un recurso valioso en el mundo empresarial. Establecemos plazos concretos para lograr resultados medibles y evaluamos constantemente nuestro progreso utilizando sistemas de medición en tiempo real. 

Comunicación y Transparencia: Creemos firmemente que la comunicación abierta y la transparencia son la clave para el éxito conjunto. Trabajamos en estrecha colaboración contigo, manteniéndote informado en cada paso del proceso.
Somos tu socio estratégico comprometido con el crecimiento de tu empresa. Juntos, transformamos datos en resultados, plazos en logros y comunicación en éxito.

Optimización de Motores de Búsqueda (SEO): Mejorar la visibilidad de tu sitio web en los resultados de búsqueda orgánica para aumentar el tráfico y la autoridad de la marca.

Automatización de Marketing: Implementación de herramientas y flujos de trabajo para automatizar tareas de marketing, como el seguimiento de leads y la segmentación de audiencia.

(CRO): Mejora continua de las páginas web y los flujos de conversión para aumentar la proporción de visitantes que se convierten en clientes.
